title: Do You Know What You Want?
itunes:title: Do You Know What You Want?
description:
Episode 479 - You probably have a rough idea of what you want in your life, but do you know exactly what you want in detail? The clarity of your goals will dictate whether or not you will hit them. In this episode I dive into how to get clear on what you want and how to execute a plan to get there.
